plot: Gon continues to hone his special ability by using the Enhancer, Emitter, and Transmuter aura types.

After hearing Biscuit's lecture on rock-paper-scissors, Gon decides to work on a special technique modeled off of rock-paper-scissors by using Enhancer, Emitter, and Conjurer abilities. Meanwhile, Killua leaves the game temporarily to take the Hunter Exam. While he's gone, Gon and Biscuit find learn about the Bomber's most recent attack.—paulp1988
